<img src="http://www.boulevards.com/images/resc/cleardot.gif" alt="" width="0" height="0" align="left" border="0">


<span class="plugtext">A delightful European-style boutique hotel located in the heart of San Francisco, the Hotel Britton is fast becoming the favorite lodging of experienced travelers from around the world.  Plantation shutters, decorative ceiling fans, and antique-style furnishings provide the Hotel Britton with the charm and d&eacute;cor of an Old World hostelry.</span></p>

<p>Guests enjoy both an evening wine tasting in The Hotel Britton's stylishly appointed lobby and the fabulous New York-style pizza served in the SOMA pizza caf&eacute;.</p>

<p>An ideal location for San Francisco visitors, the Hotel Britton is just a short walk to Union Square, Yerba Buena Gardens, the Moscone Convention Center, and first class restaurants and shopping. The world famous Fishermen's Wharf, Golden Gate Bridge, cable cars, and Chinatown are all just minutes away. Add a friendly, attentive staff and the Britton becomes one of San Francisco's most inviting boutique hotels.</p>



