<td valign="top">







<img src="gifs/room-top.jpg" width="300" height="195" align="left" alt="Hotel Britton San Francisco">

<span class="plugtext">The Britton Hotel offers 79 charming boutique guest rooms and suites, each with lovely pewter headboards, plantation shutters, and a unique personality.</span>

<p>Dine at the City's most unique pizza restaurant and enjoy original New York style pizza that's crunchy on the outside and chewy on the inside. Homemade crust, special spice blend, and fresh quality ingredients make SOMA Pizza a San Francisco favorite. The fabulous three-dimensional "ceiling of San Francisco" and mouth-watering food make this an unforgettable San Francisco dining experience.<br clear="left"></p>

<p><b>Britton Hotel Features:</b><p>

<ul class="plugtext">
<li> In-room coffee maker</li>
<li> Pay-per-view movies and Nintendo 64 video games</li>
<li> Hairdryer and iron available</li>
<li> Data port telephone with voice mail</li>
</ul>

